This is how to has_close_elements of numbers and threshold:
  Remember that i is 0
  Do this numbers's length times:
    Remember that j is sum of i and 1
    Do this diff of numbers's length and sum of i and 1 times:
      Remember that first is item i in numbers
      Remember that second is item j in numbers
      Remember that gap is abs of diff of first and second
      When gap is less than threshold, then:
        The answer is 1
      End when
      Increase j by 1
    End do
    Increase i by 1
  End do
  The answer is 0
